= Emergence

Emergence, is the original planet that theLuminous founders landed upon when moving their technology and research off Earth. It is considered a paradise planet as it has living conditions similar to that of Earth, and doesn’t require technology such as life support systems or modification of the atmosphere to live.

It contains several cities in various climates:
- Haven (capital)
- Solace
- Arden
- Kera
- Lowtide
- Vale

